  "description": "The breathing pad. LFO1 at the sacred 0.067 Hz — one full breath every 15 seconds — modulates filter cutoff for a living, respiratory texture. Wide stereo with unison spread at 0.8. Shimmer tail adds altitude. The Guru says: the physiological LFO is the oldest trick in synthesis because it maps to the oldest rhythm in the body.",
